{"id":253362,"date":"2025-05-20T10:30:57","date_gmt":"2025-05-20T08:30:57","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/?p=253362"},"modified":"2025-05-15T14:55:35","modified_gmt":"2025-05-15T12:55:35","slug":"methode-pyramide-inversee-redaction-seo","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/ressources\/content-marketing\/methode-pyramide-inversee-redaction-seo\/","title":{"rendered":"La m\u00e9thode de la pyramide invers\u00e9e pour la r\u00e9daction SEO"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"wpb-content-wrapper\"><p>[vc_row full_width=&#8221;stretch_row&#8221; my=&#8221;aucun&#8221; el_class=&#8221;hero hero-type-ressources hero-type-ressources-article&#8221;][vc_column]<div class=\"text-bloc bcrumbs\"><!-- Breadcrumb NavXT 7.4.1 -->\n<span property=\"itemListElement\" typeof=\"ListItem\"><a property=\"item\" typeof=\"WebPage\" title=\"Go to NOIISE.\" href=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\" class=\"home\" aria-current=\"page\"><span property=\"name\">NOIISE<\/span><\/a><meta property=\"position\" content=\"1\"><\/span>\n<\/div><div class=\"text-bloc\"><h1 class=\"titre_1\" style=\"text-align: center;\">La m\u00e9thode de la pyramide invers\u00e9e pour la r\u00e9daction SEO<\/h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">20 mai 2025 &#8211; Nicolas Pirio <br> <span class=\"update_date\">Date de mise \u00e0 jour : 15 mai 2025<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><ul class=\"post_tags\"><li  style=\"background-color: rgba(254, 17, 120, .1); color: rgba(254, 17, 120); padding: 0.45rem 1.6rem; border-radius: 25px; margin-right: 8px; font-weight: 500; transition: background-color 300ms ease, color 300ms ease; display: block;\">Content Marketing<\/li><li  style=\"background-color: rgba(29, 99, 239, .1); color: rgba(29, 99, 239); padding: 0.45rem 1.6rem; border-radius: 25px; margin-right: 8px; font-weight: 500; transition: background-color 300ms ease, color 300ms ease; display: block;\">SEO<\/li><\/ul><\/p>\n<\/div>[\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_section el_class=&#8221;content-ressource&#8221;][vc_row el_class=&#8221;content-article&#8221;][vc_column]<div class=\"text-bloc liste-puce-bleu\"><p><strong>La pyramide invers\u00e9e<\/strong> est une <strong>technique d\u2019\u00e9criture journalistique<\/strong> consistant \u00e0 <strong>fournir les informations essentielles en tout d\u00e9but de page<\/strong> avant de d\u00e9tailler le sujet. Peu utilis\u00e9e, cette technique r\u00e9pond souvent tr\u00e8s bien aux attentes et aux besoins des internautes et est donc <strong>parfaite pour le r\u00e9f\u00e9rencement SEO<\/strong>. Appliquer la technique de la pyramide invers\u00e9e en r\u00e9daction web permet de <strong>maximiser l\u2019impact SEO d\u2019un contenu<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<\/div>[\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row el_class=&#8221;content-article article-table-matiere&#8221;][vc_column]<div class=\"text-bloc toc\"><p class=\"titre_3\">Table des mati\u00e8res<\/p>\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_74 ez-toc-wrap-center counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-custom ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\" style=\"cursor:inherit\">Sommaire<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" aria-label=\"Toggle Table of Content\"><span class=\"ez-toc-js-icon-con\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\"